{
  "stem": "2170.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I thought I would run away again because I don't want to be in the ghetto because if we are-- we saw the Germans already with trucks coming in , coming in.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I took a-- a girl, she was my age, and her parents said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You go away from the ghetto, another town, which was another 10 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that town they call it Stanislavchik.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as it was still cold, there was snow over there, and it's still cold until May.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in March.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got dressed, and she got dressed like a little Christian girl.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she took a-- a chicken with her, a live chicken, and I took some eggs, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we knew if-- if on the road the Germans going to catch us, we're gonna give them this, maybe they're not gonna shoot us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as we were going out from the city of Zhmerinka, we going with the railroad tracks into that other town, snow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as we come out from the town, I see already Germans with a [? rig ?] over their helms in battle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In front I look, I see artillery, antiaircraft artillery, all kind of artillery, already digged in, waiting for the Russians to come.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I walked with her running, we were walking actually, and I see these German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was a feldgendarmerie with a big black steal over here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, halt, stop, as we come near.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says in German, [SPEAKING GERMAN], what do you have over here?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she says I have a kuritsa, I have a chicken.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said I have eggs, ei-- eier, eggs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said, OK, give it to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she gave him this.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
